              it. Credits: Justin Hamel/Bloomberg/Getty Images</i
            >
          </p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            President Trump announced a series of significant tariff hikes
            targeting key trading partners and industries. Brazil will face a
            <a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #4d3060;
                color: black;
              "
              href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-31-jul-25-spotlight-h1-1-50-tariff-on-selected-exports?source=website"
              target="_blank"
              >50% tariff on selected exports</a
            >
            in what Trump described as retaliation for the treatment of his
            ally, right-wing former Brazilian President Jair Bolsonaro (who
            faces multiple criminal investigations).
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">
            Meanwhile, a
            <a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #4d3060;
                color: black;
              "
              href="https://link.presidentialsummary.com/ps-31-jul-25-spotlight-h1-2-revised-agreement-with-south-korea?source=website"
              target="_blank"
              >revised agreement with South Korea</a
            >
            raises tariffs from 10% to 15% across most sectors, sidestepping an
            earlier proposal for a 25%. Trump said the agreement includes a
            $350B funding pledge from South Korea for US-controlled projects.
            Seoul also committed to purchasing $100B worth of US energy over 3.5
            years.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; filter: blur(5px)">
            In a broader move, Trump imposed a 50% tariff on all semi-finished
            copper and related products. The ‚Äú<a
              style="
                text-decoration: none;
                border-bottom: 2px solid #4d3060;
                color: black;
