              target="_blank"
              >de minimis</a
            >‚Äù rule, which previously allowed low-value goods to enter the US
            duty-free, has also been suspended for all countries. This change
            directly impacts express-shipping platforms like Shein and Temu,
            whose low-cost parcels had avoided import duties under existing
            exemptions.
          </p>
        </mj-text>
